# Daily Ops Revenue Drilldown

- Keep the Daily Ops dashboard snapshot-first. Dashboard metric GET paths should read `daily_ops_snapshot*` or precomputed Daily Ops revenue helpers, not live Bork/Eitje raw aggregation.
- Add revenue drilldown data through small builder modules under `server/utils/dailyOpsSnapshot/`; avoid growing `fetchDashboardBundle.ts` with feature-specific aggregation details.
- Render this feature below `DailyOpsProfitHourCard` in `components/daily-ops/DailyOpsRevenueMetricsSection.vue`.
- Keep UI modular: one parent drilldown section plus focused table/chart/top-list components.
- Missing snapshot data must render empty states or coverage notes; do not hide gaps with unexpected live fallbacks.
- Preserve existing dashboard totals: venue strip revenue, summary total, and P&L interval revenue must continue to match.
